<p style="max-width: 450px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 300;">Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</p>

<p style="max-width: 450px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 300;">Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.</p>

<p style="max-width: 450px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 300;"><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, :reset_password_token => @resource.reset_password_token), :style => "text-decoration: none; color: #0088cc;" %></p>

<p style="max-width: 450px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 300;">If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p style="max-width: 450px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 300;">Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
</div>